header.gameNote: SUN BELT CONFERENCE MEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - FINAL

videos.description: UT Arlington's David Azore rises up and banks in the elbow jumper off the glass.
videos.headline: Azore nails the elbow jumper

videos.description: Malik Benlevi sinks in the deep 3-pointer to give Georgia State a 64-52 lead with 5:02 left in the game.
videos.headline: Benlevi knocks down the deep 3

videos.description: Georgia State tops UT Arlington 73-64 for the Sun Belt Tournament Championship and a NCAA tournament berth.
videos.headline: Georgia State captures the Sun Belt and NCAA tourney bid
